Package: hashmyfiles
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Jegly <jegly@hashmyfiles>
Installed-Size: 1058
Depends: libadwaita-1-0 (>= 1.2~alpha), libc6 (>= 2.39), libgcc-s1 (>= 4.2), libglib2.0-0t64 (>= 2.54.0), libgtk-4-1 (>= 4.9.2)
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/jegly/hashmyfiles
Description: File integrity scanner and verifier
 HashMyFiles scans files and generates cryptographic hash databases
 (SHA-256, SHA-512, BLAKE3) for integrity verification. Features
 multi-threaded scanning, interactive diff viewer, and export to
 TXT/JSON/CSV formats.
 .
 Created by Jegly.
